snippet.title: I Made a Stressful Farming Simulator in 3 Days! (The Great Autumn Game Jam Devlog)
snippet.description:
I Made a Stressful Farming Simulator in 3 Days! (The Great Autumn Game Jam)

Hello there people! In this video, I took part in The Great Autumn Game Jam and made this Farming Game!

Our Discord Server: https://discord.gg/ZPbMDPQwt7
Play the Game: https://devnugget.itch.io/3-days-tactical-farming
